name: Mr. Kiss Kiss Bang Bang
comments: Recorded as the main title theme to the Thunderball movie, with its 48 second orchestral intro timed so that the vocal commenced after the film title appeared on screen.  The recording was not used after United Artists then specified that the theme song must contain Thunderball in its lyric, requiring the hasty composition of a new theme (sung by Tom Jones).
